# Build and Testing

```bash
# Build the library (standard Rust)
cargo build --release
```

```bash
# Run tests (includes doc tests from lib.rs)
cargo test
```

Note: No explicit unit/integration test files were found in the source. Consider adding tests for `atomic`, `backup`, `lock`, `merge`, and `validate`.

# Project Structure

neuxcfg/
src/
lib.rs # Public API and Neuxcfg main struct
error.rs # NeuxcfgError enum
types.rs # GlobalConfig, ProjectConfig, ProjectInfo
atomic.rs # Atomic file write utility
backup.rs # Backup and restore functions
lock.rs # File locking (FileLock)
merge.rs # Deep merge for TOML values
validate.rs # Extra field validator
